{"data":[{"id":561140190,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0f21a177f318b5efb11cb41f263fa061","url_token":"xie-dian-feng","name":"廖尔","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/06bf6627c8bb545728216c3646432494_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/06bf6627c8bb545728216c3646432494_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0f21a177f318b5efb11cb41f263fa061","user_type":"people","headline":"一个普通的中国人","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561140190","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-637ac7db5ca780a51a5b5f4aed5724a2_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545920531,"updated_time":1545920531,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":2,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e那是肯定的，我个人认为。因为这是数学届的王冠 ，有些数学家穷尽一生的心血也没能把它证明过证伪，比如陈景润先生，他虽然有所成就，但还是未能把它攻破，就连当年哥德巴赫写信给欧拉请教这个问题，欧拉先生也表示了沉默，好像不久后就去世了，我没记错的话！我觉得如果能解决这一问题，一是能获得数学届的诺贝尔奖——菲尔兹奖，据说或了这个奖，这个人去任何一所高校任教，工资不得低于不知具体几十万的，如果现实一点，他可以去当个老师，边继续学术研究，边养家糊口，了却余生……不管怎样，我觉得高中生要证明哥德巴赫猜想确实是件不容易的事，起码要有下图中的裁缝那样认真、执着才行！！！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f3780b29e933004bf75238684648e2a5_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1125\" data-rawheight=\"1644\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-075bae74291a1891bf6124d65351acf4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1125\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-f3780b29e933004bf75238684648e2a5_r.jpg\"\u003e\u